r only seldom.  But I wish to do a little bit better in status. I was happy=
 when other musicians or students got praise - I just wanted a little more.=
 And in romantic affairs, second place is no place, so it is hard to wish o=
thers success with mates we at least had on our list of possibles.</span></=
